&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Serve as a first point of contact for routine client inquiries via different channels of communication and issue resolution, escalating more complex issues as needed. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Apply standard professional concepts and guidelines to process transactions, maintain client records, and ensure regulatory compliance. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Execute daily, weekly, and monthly reporting tasks, identifying basic variances and following established processes to resolve discrepancies. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Collaborate with internal teams (Accounting, Cash Ops, IT) to ensure timely and accurate delivery of client outputs, building stable working relationships across teams. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Follow structured workflows to support documentation, procedures, and consistent service delivery, contributing to incremental process improvements. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Use approved AI-enabled tools in a limited and controlled manner to enhance efficiency (e.g., drafting communications, summarizing data, or organizing information), while ensuring accuracy, compliance, and human oversight. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Maintain a high level of organization, attention to detail, and adherence to established policies and procedures. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Provide coverage for team members and support broader team objectives as needed.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
