&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Reporting to the VP of Total Rewards, Onboarding &amp;amp; Culture, this role operates with significant independence across a broad portfolio of onboarding and engagement work, exercising judgment on complex assignments and escalating strategically. The HR Generalist brings deep functional knowledge, cross-functional influence, and a disciplined approach to program design — translating organizational context into onboarding tracks and engagement touchpoints that accelerate new hire productivity and build belonging from day one.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
